<facsimile><graphic url="https://www.e-manuscripta.ch/bau/content/titleinfo/1063916"/></facsimile><text><body><div type="letter">
<pb facs="1063917" n="1"/>
<note>1715 Febr. 27 /129</note>
<opener><lb/><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> Viro <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></opener>
<p><lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1156361761" type="person">Sebastianus Checozzi</rs> <abbr>Doctiss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Hermanni</rs>
<lb/>vestri Discipulus dedit solutionem proble<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>matis Itali<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Geometris a Te propositi, quam
    <lb/><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_P88RGPV8">solutionem</rs> excerptam ex Diarii nostri Tomo
         <lb/>vigesimo tertio ad Vos transmittere oper<unclear><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></unclear>
<lb/>pretium duxi in eum fin<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ut possitis aliquid
    <lb/>rescribere si lubebit. Crastina die tradam <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_DHVYFVAZ">res<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ponsionem</rs> tuam doctissimam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me in Tusca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nam linguam versam Diarii nostri Auto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ribus ut eam inserant eiusdem Diarii To<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo vigesimo quarto <subst><del>quid</del><add>qui</add></subst> propediem in
             <lb/>publicum prodibit. Brevi fiet electio ter<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tii <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatoris</rs> <rs type="organisation">Archylicei Patavini</rs>, qui uti
         <lb/>spero erit unus ex meis Mecenatibus. Statim
             <lb/>ac erit facta electio de <subst><del>S</del><add>T</add></subst>ui promotione solli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>citus ero. Interim sperare licet exitum felicem,
         <lb/>et tempore opus est. Sub finem Quadrage<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, vel post festa paschalia expectabo
             <lb/>adventum <abbr>Doctiss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Nicolai</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> Tui <unclear>F</unclear>ilii
             <lb/>pro quo omnia parata erunt.</p>
<closer><salute>Interim ipsi
         <pb facs="1063918" n="2"/>
<lb/>et <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patri</rs> suo nunquam satis laudato salutem
         <lb/>plurimam meo nomine dicito,
         <lb/>meque amare perge.</salute>
<lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1715-02-28">Secundo Calendas Martias 
    <lb/>MDCCXV</date> more Veneto.</dateline></closer><note type="editorial">Anm. Otto Spiess in seiner Transkription: Secundo ungewöhnlich für pridie; es handelt sich also um den 28. II. 1715. Da in Venedig das Jahr mit dem 1. März begann, galt dieser Tag als letzter des Jahres 1714.</note>
</div></body></text></TEI>